w README.md <<'EOF'
# HELIXNID Code Studio
Standalone Mac desktop coding-agent IDE. Not a VS Code extension.

## Lock
Renderer has no fs/path/electron/child_process. Preload exposes only safe `window.helix` APIs. Writes require approved patch + hash check + rollback + ledger.

## Run
```bash
npm install
npm run typecheck
npm run build
npm audit --omit=dev
npm run dev
```

## Final label
HELIXNID_CODE_STUDIO_FULL_DESKTOP_AGENT_IDE_LOCK
EOF

